quest.paths module

quest.paths.get_path()[source]

Determines the base path of the application.

If the application is running in a frozen state (e.g., packaged with PyInstaller), it returns the directory containing the executable. Otherwise, it returns the directory containing the current script.

Returns:

The base path of the application.

Return type:

str
